entries.title_d: Hunt down and destroy Valarian operatives
entries.title: Tatooine System: Hunt Down and Destroy Valarian Operatives
entries.split_quest_alert_fail: \#pcontrast3 Nirame: < \#pcontrast1 He is right on top of you, take action. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast3 Nirame: < \#pcontrast1 About that freighter we wanted: It is in route to Endor, perhaps you can convince them to alter course. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_location_d: Valarian controlled space in the Tatooine System
entries.quest_escort_d: Important to this mission, all Valarian craft must be destroyed.
entries.failed_escape: \#pcontrast3 Tacticle Computer: < \#pcontrast3 Warning! Hyperspace signature detected in close proximity. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_wiped_out: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 All escorting craft have been destroyed. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.escort_remaining: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 All escorting craft have been destroyed, %DI remaining. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.destroy_escort: \#pcontrast3 Primary objective destroyed, finish off any remaining escort craft. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.assassinate_success: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Target objective has been destroyed. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_2: \#pcontrast3 Tactical Computer: < \#pcontrast1 Target craft identified. Tracking... \#pcontrast3 >
entries.arrival_phase_1: \#pcontrast3 Nirame: < \#pcontrast3 I'm sending you the target information, one of Valarias stooges.  Be quick about this, I will have more for you shortly. \#pcontrast3 >
